Alchemy is the art of making potions, available to shamans at L25. The intelligence stat may improve the rate of success. Potions are made by placing the components in a medicine bag (available at the shaman's guild for about 2p) and clicking the COMBINE button. Potions cannot be used while moving. Lesser (or minor) potions have a shorter duration than their regular or greater equivalents. Potions will not stack with each other; however, each seems to stack with regular buffs, and a few potions interact provided stats do not overlap. Drinking another identical potion will cancel the effects of the previous. Potions have the same limitations as the spell; i.e., shrink can only be used in a dungeon, SoW can only be used outdoors. <br>
